{"tid":1255574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★政Whats噏：惡鬥游蕙禎　植潔鈴笑住道歉反擊","createTime":"2019-06-24T14:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:09:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"292e28cff77763c31588e00540ef505de7ab826f","tid":1255574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"因宣誓風波而被褫奪立法會議席嘅青年新政游蕙禎，尋日(23日)喺網上公布遭有小花之稱嘅東區區議員植潔鈴盜用相片，更公開埋對話錄音證明植潔鈴認衰。不過，事件去到今日(24日)仍有下文，兩女再度出手交鋒。<br />\n<br />\n話說今晨植潔鈴拍片，解釋話玩通訊軟件Telegram唔用真名同真相係常識，揀相時「好好彩」揀中游蕙禎，重申自己唔知係游而向佢道歉。不過話題一轉，植就笑住話游蕙禎已有一排無露面，暗寸佢潛水多時而唔認得佢，又話張相如網民所言，似某位男演員咁Man，說話相當有骨喎。<br />\n<br />\n至於游蕙禎都唔係省油的燈，佢就喺Facebook話建制派淪落到同本土派道歉係陰公，叫植下次唔好咁話，更稱對方做「游區議員」添<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190624/bkn-20190624175549395-0624_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190624%2Fbkn-20190624175549395-0624_00822_001.html&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=52c540d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190624/bkn-20190624175549395-0624_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"08fbaf5c1234636b613882484746e112af38f68c","tid":1255574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cU61NZh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcU61NZh.png&h=bacbd29b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"971768682ac8d4e4c7b6caf3d2a176b23bbc67b2","tid":1255574,"uid":168675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca60021971b62c15e7929bfe32457e0f32cee080","tid":1255574,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\